data.name: ImagePosition
desc: specifies the position of an image, relative to another object

items.name: LeftTop
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned at the left of, and top-aligned to, the other object

items.name: LeftCenter
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned at the left of, and vertically centered to, the other object

items.name: LeftBottom
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned at the left of, and bottom-aligned to, the other object

items.name: RightTop
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned at the right of, and top-aligned to, the other object

items.name: RightCenter
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned at the right of, and vertically centered to, the other object

items.name: RightBottom
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned at the right of, and bottom-aligned to, the other object

items.name: AboveLeft
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned above and left-aligned to the other object

items.name: AboveCenter
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned above and horizontally centered to the other object

items.name: AboveRight
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned above and right-aligned to the other object

items.name: BelowLeft
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned below and left-aligned to the other object

items.name: BelowCenter
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned below and horizontally centered to the other object

items.name: BelowRight
lines: specifies that the image should be positioned below and right-aligned centered to the other object

items.name: Centered
lines: specifies that the image should be horizontally and vertically centered to the other object.
